=========================
 WWE 2K25 - Xbox Controls
=========================

Create FSA(finite state automata) machine for states and connect(by keys)

üéÆ BASIC MOVEMENT
------------------
Left Stick        -    Move
Right Stick       -    Change Face/Target/opponent direction
LT (Hold)         -    Run
LB (Near Ropes)   -    Enter/Exit Ring
LB (Corner)       -    Climb Turnbuckle
LB (Near Object)  -    Pick Up
LB (Near Table)   -    Set Up

üëä STRIKES & COMBOS
---------------------
X                - Light Attack (Strike)
Hold X           - Heavy Attack
X ‚Üí X / Y / A    - Combo Chain
X/Y/A (Last)     - Combo Ender
RT + X/Y         - Grapple Strike (from grapple stance)

üí• GRAPPLES
------------
B                - Grapple (Front/Rear)
RT + A/X/Y       - Grapple Move
RT + LS + A      - Directional Grapple
RS ‚Üë (In Grapple)- Turn Opponent Around

üìâ IRISH WHIPS & CARRY
------------------------
B (Tap)          - Irish Whip
B (Hold) + LS    - Strong Irish Whip
RB + LS          - Carry Opponent (grapple first)
B (Tap While Carrying) - Slam Opponent

üß® FINISHERS & SIGNATURES
---------------------------
RT + Y           - Finisher (if bar is full)
RT + X           - Signature (if bar is full)
LT + RT          - Charge Finisher

‚õî REVERSALS & BLOCKING
-------------------------
Y (Tap)          - Reversal (Strike/Grapple)
RT               - Block
RT + Y           - Reversal (Heavy/Finisher)
RT + LS          - Dodge (directional)

üåÄ SPECIAL MOVES
------------------
RT + LS Up (Grapple)    - Lift opponent
A (when opponent down)  - Pin
X (when opponent down)  - Ground Strike
B (when opponent down)  - Pick Up
LB (next to ladder/chair) - Interact

‚ö° SPRINGBOARDS & DIVES
-------------------------
Run + LB (near ropes/corner) - Springboard Attack
LS toward ropes + X (top rope) - Dive Outside
LB (Holding Object)           - Use Weapon

üì¶ OBJECTS / LADDER / TABLE
------------------------------
LB (Near Object)      - Pick Up
LB (Near Table)       - Set Up
RT + LS (at Table)    - Position
X/Y/A (with Object)   - Use Object Attack

üéØ TARGETING
-------------
RS (Click)            - Change Target (multi-opponent)
D-Pad Up/Down/Left/Right - Taunts / Crowd Interaction

=========================
  BONUS TIPS
=========================
‚úî RT = Grapple Modifier / Block
‚úî Y = Reversal / Counter
‚úî Combos are Fast & Unpredictable
‚úî Use Signature to earn Finisher faster
‚úî Customize everything in ‚ÄúMove Set‚Äù Menu